# Raise Node's heap ceiling for the dev server and build.
# Node defaults to ~4 GB old-space regardless of physical RAM, and this large
# Docusaurus site (600+ docs, 190+ blog posts) now exceeds it during `docusaurus
# start`. node-options propagates NODE_OPTIONS to every node process pnpm spawns
# (pnpm run AND pnpm exec), so the limit applies no matter how the server is launched.
node-options=--max-old-space-size=8192
